day cake.\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 471, \"end\": 476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.5858192713284752e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"back-to-back mountain bike Olympics titles\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"a brief visit\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the house\", \"from\": 434, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"his parents\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 455}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"some cards\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 509}, {\"ngram\": \"the candles\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"his birthday cake\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his attention was almost immediately shifting to the prospect of an unlikely double in the road race on Saturday.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his attention\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"the road race\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 662}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For most, the thought would be an impossibility but such is Pidcock's versatility - not to mention the manner in which he pulled off the gold on Monday - that anything is possible.\", \"from\": 677, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the thought\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"an impossibility\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock's versatility\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"the manner\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the space of a few weeks, he has gone from vying for stage wins in the Tour de France to switching to mountain biking and then back onto the road.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 933, \"end\": 947, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999480755889385, \"rank\": 5.0164135550655874e-05, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the space\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 871}, {\"ngram\": \"a few weeks\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"stage wins\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"mountain biking\", \"from\": 964, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about his goal in the immediate aftermath of his gold, he said: \\\"I am too tired to think about that.\\\"\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his goal\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"the immediate aftermath\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"his gold\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And with good reason.\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good reason\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1139}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pidcock had been the overwhelming favourite to come away with themountain bikegold and lived up to the pre-race billing as he pulled away from the field before a puncture.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1312, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the overwhelming favourite\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"themountain bikegold\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"the pre-race billing\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"a puncture\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A miscommunication meant his mechanic was initially unaware and the delay cost Pidcock around half a minute.\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A miscommunication\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"his mechanic\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"the delay\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"around half a minute\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It had echoes of Josh Tarling in the men's individual time trial back in the Parisian rain on Sunday but, while Tarling struggled to wrestle back too much time, Pidcock picked up rider after rider in his pursuit of gold.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"score\": 0.9898697568777295, \"rank\": 0.010141046559404973, \"text\": \"Josh\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josh_Lyman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"echoes\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's individual time trial\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1488}, {\"ngram\": \"the Parisian rain\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"Tarling\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1543}, {\"ngram\": \"too much time\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1583}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 1585, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"rider\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"his pursuit\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he looked remarkably calm in the process.\", \"from\": 1645, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table: Latest count today after Team GB rush on day three Olympics 2024 complete schedule: Date and time for every event He said: \\\"There is no point in stressing over it is there?\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9998596819389076, \"rank\": 0.00014030012748323224, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"Latest count\", \"from\": 1719, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympics 2024 complete schedule\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"Date\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"every event\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"no point\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's not going to help me get back to the front.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What's the point in stressing?\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had enough stress this week.\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough stress\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2000}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But 30 seconds is a lot on this course.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"30 seconds\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"this course\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was not easy.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I had someone telling me I was in eighth.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2084}, {\"ngram\": \"eighth\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not give a f*** what position I was in.\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2158, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a f\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"what position\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to know how far it is in front.\\\"\", \"from\": 2159, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finally made his way to the front with an audacious move past home favourite Victor Koretzky, the pair briefly barging shoulders as Pidcock shot past and his French rival lost his rhythm.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2282, \"end\": 2297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\", \"score\": 0.9999880939516794, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Victor Koretzky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Koretzky\"}, {\"begin\": 2363, \"end\": 2369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9625940021846103, \"rank\": 0.013899073330462874, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2225}, {\"ngram\": \"the front\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"an audacious move\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulders\", \"from\": 2324, \"to\": 2333}, {\"ngram\": \"Pidcock\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"his rhythm\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It led to boos from the partisan crowd both at the finish and on the podium afterwards.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"boos\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"the partisan crowd\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the French crowd turning on him, he said: \\\"The boos are a shame because that's not really the spirit of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2483, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2490, \"end\": 2496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9625940021846103, \"rank\": 0.013899073330462874, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The boos\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"a shame\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"the spirit\", \"from\": 2576, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2602}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I do understand that the French are very passionate, they wanted Victor to win.\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2633, \"end\": 2639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9625940021846103, \"rank\": 0.013899073330462874, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Victor\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That was understandable.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They did not boo the rock that made me puncture!\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the rock\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I did not do anything wrong.\\\"\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he was adamant he had done nothing wrong, a racing manoeuvre and one backed by the officials in the immediate aftermath.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2837}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2895}, {\"ngram\": \"the immediate aftermath\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said: \\\"I came here to win and that is all I was thinking about.\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are so special, it is bigger than cycling, so you never give up and you give everything.\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3082, \"to\": 3092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew if I stayed closer to Victory then I could make a move in the last part where he wasn't expecting it.\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Victory\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3132}, {\"ngram\": \"a move\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"the last part\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He left a gap and I had to take it.\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3240, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gap\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's what I have always done and the Olympics are no different.\\\"\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3305, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3274, \"to\": 3286}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It begged the question of whether he might try for the hat-trick of titles in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 3307, \"to\": 3397, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3396, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999893143469, \"rank\": 7.916324797640205e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the question\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"the hat-trick\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3371}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exhausted after a remarkable ride to gold, he understandably said, \\\"That I can not answer now.\\\"\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a remarkable ride\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3431}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news 3 UK Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war 4 Lifestyle Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026 5 Football Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3555, \"end\"